{"id": 1044, "title": "Ticket #1044: The gridmanager needs to be aware of X509UserProxyFQAN", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe gridmanager needs to be aware of VOMS attributes in job proxies, as they can affect authentication with remote servers and what local user a job is mapped to on those servers. Some parts of the gridmanager still need to deal with just the proxy subject, and the FQAN isn't always available, so a blanket replacement of FQAN for subject won't work.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2009-Dec-15 16:16:11 by jfrey:</em> <br/>\n\nPushed a fix to V7_4_1-branch for 7.4.1.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3356\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3356'); return false;\" title=\"Gridmanager crash when cream job has VOMS-less proxy\">#3356</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nGridmanager crash when cream job has VOMS-less proxy</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2009-Dec-16 14:34</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/4adc35f7550aeac5f75ebd0b63aaefc933a6efc7\">[16683]</a></span>: Fix X509 attributes in gridmanager ads with voms attributes. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1044\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1044'); return false;\" title=\"The gridmanager needs to be aware of X509UserProxyFQAN\">#